{
  "texts": [
    "Interestingly, the authors experiment on cluttered and non-cluttered environments which is a shared characteristic of production environments -namely the variation of clutter between different sets.",
    "Nägeli et al. (2017) directly address this problem and further highlight challenges with dynamic entities (drones, humans, moving set etc.",
    "), using model predicted contour control (MPCC).",
    "14 Confronted with a highly constrained scenario, the authors simplify the problem using manually defined \"virtual rails\" for each drone.",
    "This acts as a coarse trajectory guide that drones loosely follow to avoid collisions while achieving one-shot aesthetic objectives."
  ]
}